# Example crontab entries for OpenClaw issues snapshot automation
#
# Install with:
#   crontab -e
# Then paste one of the schedules below.

# 1) Recommended: daily auto mode (weekly full + daily delta)
#    - Runs every day at 02:15 local time
15 2 * * * /home/box/.openclaw/workspace/openclaw-lighthouse/research/openclaw-issues-snapshot/scripts/run_snapshot.sh auto

# 2) Optional explicit weekly full (Sunday 03:10)
#10 3 * * 0 /home/box/.openclaw/workspace/openclaw-lighthouse/research/openclaw-issues-snapshot/scripts/run_snapshot.sh full
